About CentOS:

The Community ENTerprise Operating System (CentOS) Linux is a community-supported enterprise distribution derived from sources freely provided to the public by Red Hat. As such CentOS Linux aims to be functionally compatible with Red Hat Enterprise Linux. The CentOS Project is the organization that builds CentOS. We mainly change packages to remove upstream vendor branding and artwork.

For information on CentOS please visit the CentOS website.

column2: learn English. It helps us to learn how to communicate our ideas/expressions with others easily. It is a complete App and useful for everyone. We get to learn new words and how to pronounce them.

EMILLY is helping us to learn English. EMILLY is a perfect tool to master the spoken English. The aim of this app is to make us a confident English speaker through various engaging activities in a fun and easy manner.
EMILLY is awesome amazing fun & entertaining resource which gives us confidence and motivates us to speak English fluently. Those who want to learn English in an easy way should use EMILLY.

EMILLY is a good application and helps us to gain fluency in English. When I started learning this language I was very confused to choose appropriate materials or institutes. However now I can say that if anyone wants to learn English then he/she should use this application. It is very easy and we can use the given techniques real time.

Learning English is no more hard and confusing. I say this because I have used an application called “EMILLY” which has cleared all my doubts & fear related to speaking English. It is an easy application and anyone can understand & learn English easily with the help of it. Thanks EMILLY!!!!!!!

I want to thank EMILLY for the guidance it gave me to speak fluent English. EMILLY helps us to correct our mistakes by practicing on various learning modules. Now I am very comfortable in English due to EMILLY.

कमाल का अनुभव!!! अंग्रेजी सीखने के लिए एक अद्भुत और आसान app EMILLY है। मुझे लगता है कि यह शिक्षार्थियों के विभिन्न स्तर के लिए एक आदर्श App है। इससे हमें आत्म-विश्वास प्राप्त होता है तथा अँग्रेजी बोल-चाल में सुधार आता है। यह App उपयोग मे बहुत आसान है। मैं व्यक्तिगत रूप से आपको धन्यवाद देता हूँ की इस भाषा को सीखने में आपने मेरी मदद की और मेरा सही मार्ग दर्शन किया।

EMILLY is helping us to learn English language as we can learn practice and evaluate our knowledge here itself. I am satisfied with the content and methodology which EMILLY is using to teach us. Thank you so much EMILLY.

अंग्रेजी वर्तमान युग में हमारे जीवन का बहुत महत्वपूर्ण हिस्सा है | इसीलिए मैं अपनी अंग्रेजी सुधारना चाहती थी और तभी मैंने EMILLY app के बारे में सुना और उसे तुरंत डाउनलोड किया | दोस्तों विश्वास कीजिये ये एक बहुत ही अच्छी app है इसने मेरा विश्वास बढ़ाया और मैं आब कहीं भी किसी का भी सामना करने में सक्षम हूँ | मैंने इस app से व्याकरण शब्दकोश आदि बहुत सी चीजें सीखी और इस app ने मेरी जिंदगी बदल दी |

| कुछ दिन पहले मुझे EMILLY app के बारे में पता चला | इस एप्लिकेशन का उपयोग करके मैं अपने संचार में सुधार करने में सक्षम था| अब मैं धाराप्रवाह बिना किसी हिचकिचाहट के दूसरों के सामने अंग्रेजी बोल सकता हूँ | मेरा सुझाव है कि हर किसी को इस एप्लिकेशन का प्रयोग करना चाहिए| अंत में मैं EMILLY को धन्यवाद देना चाहता हूँ कि उसने मेरी जिंदगी बदली और दुनिया का सामना करना सिखाया |

This is the default welcome page used to test the correct

If you can read this page  it means that the Apache HTTP server installed at

If you are a normal user of this web site and don't know what this page is

If the problem persists  please contact the site's administrator.

found by accessing the manual if the apache2-doc
package was installed on this server.

The default Ubuntu document root is <tt>/var/www/html</tt>. You

to previous releases which provides better security out of the box.

• 服务于校园学生及组织成员

column1: 产品价值观：每日新生，来日可期
十年技术积累，铸就行业领先水平，构建品牌效应，成为客户最爱产品
以提升组织产能为整体目标，以战略能力、协作关系、组织知识、企业文化等无形资产和能力为核心管理要素
思维前瞻、架构领先、经验丰富，集运行、开发、集成和运维于一体的专业解决方案
组织门户
<div class="modal fade" id="project-1" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-1-label" aria-hidden="true">
组织门户作为组织IT架构的统一展现层，可为用户提供基于角色的个性化工作视图。通过领导驾驶舱、部门工作门户、个人工作门户、协同工具、统一搜索中心、统一用户身份认证平台、统一用户身份管理平台的建设，帮助用户更快、更方便、更安全的浏览同个人相关的信息、数据、应用资源，帮助用户更高效的完成一天的工作。
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
公文管理
<div class="modal fade" id="project-2" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-2-label" aria-hidden="true">
打破组织内部各部门、科室间的信息壁垒，通过文件发布、订阅、推荐等功能，实现文档信息的快速流转，保障文件完整性与时效性
根据办公需求固化文件审批流程，实现高效的公文流转、在线审批，加强各部门、科室间的信息联系，提升办公效率
安全、高效的一键分享与发布，实现信息实时传递与通知，避免信息滞后，同时加强外部访问的监管控制
支持文件水印、电子签章等功能，将纸质审批电子化
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
公务管理
<div class="modal fade" id="project-3" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-3-label" aria-hidden="true">
无缝流转，跨部门协同再也不用跑断腿
公务的使用场景不再局限于客服内部，可以一键将工单高效流转到其他部门。组织内其他业务部门也能通过发起公务流程来进行跨部门的协作沟通。
快速检索、海量信息急速到达结果，用户能够按照公务标题、公务发起人、公务审批人、公务创建时间等多维度的搜索条件查询公务。系统支持数据导出服务，以达到信息价值最大化利用。
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
行政管理
<div class="modal fade" id="project-4" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-4-label" aria-hidden="true">
行政管理模块包括员工定位、考勤管理、奖惩管理、行政事务管理、行政用品管理功能，囊括企业行政办公的所有工作事务，通过强有力的报表生成工具、分析工具、信息共享，使得企业行政管理人员有条不紊的开展繁杂的日常行政工作，降低企业用工成本，提高企业工作效率
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
日程管理
<div class="modal fade" id="project-5" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-5-label" aria-hidden="true">
基于月、周、日的日历视图，把安排到每一天的具体时间点，让每一天的时间都充分利用；同时借助于多终端的消息提醒，避免事项的遗漏。甚至您也可以把个人非工作事项也安排进来，完全是属于自己的全时间管理。
多人面试、多人一同外出拜访、会议安排等多方的场景应用，不仅仅是一个人的时间，可以快速帮助同事建立共同的事务计划安排。
若您不想公开你的时间日程安排、或者也不希望让上级查阅到日程内容，通过私密日程可以安排完全仅属于自己范围的事项。
随时随地的查阅到每位同事的时间安排（当然系统提供相应的权限控制，仅能了解到时间占用掉，但不能查阅到具体的日程内容），了解到每位同事的某段时间是否被占用，避免工作的打扰。
要想知道这位同事去哪里了、或者让同事和上级知道自己外出干嘛了，您只需公开日程即可；从团队的角度来看，也就自然而然的形成的团队成员外出动态。
主管经理等上级可以直接安排日程事项给到下级，并可以透视团队每位下属成员的每一天的具体时间安排和进展。
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
合同管理
<div class="modal fade" id="project-6" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-6-label" aria-hidden="true">
合同的每个环节、细节的数据和信息都可进行关联。
业务过程都可追溯，并且能够查看整个合同评审的流程、查看PDF合同、合同履约情况。
帮助组织更好的管理和监控合同运作流程，有效防范风险。
实现合同管理规范化、智能化。
自定义审批流程，支持会签、分支、撤回等功能，满足中国式流程的要求。
监督合同履行状态，异常处理和控制，防控履约风险。
根据合同执行情况提交合同付款申请，系统会根据申请表单自动生成拨款汇签。
对于合同结算金额变更的，部门经办人需填列合同变更申请，提交给合同管理员进行审核操作。
合同结束以后，系统将根据合同方名称自动生成关于该合同方履约情况页面。
归档信息登记，实现档案的快速查找，防止档案丢失。
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
会议管理
<div class="modal fade" id="project-7" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-7-label" aria-hidden="true">
规范固化企业日常会议管理中的会议计划、会议方案、会议通知、会议资料、决策执行等业务，同时通过与公文管理、会议室资源管理、移动视频会议、督办管理等功能进行结合，实现会前、会中、会后的一体化管控。
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
绩效管理
<div class="modal fade" id="project-8" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-8-label" aria-hidden="true">

随着商业环境和企业的不断发展，企业员工的绩效考核指标也越来越多样且随着企业的发展变化而变化。如何更好地执行企业的绩效考核计划而不是停留在形式表面，是企业绩效考核管理的难题。8Manage HCM 支持多种绩效考核模式，提供灵活的绩效考核流程设置和管理机制，支持自定义考核表和考核指标，员工之间，员工和上级之间都可以通过系统实时沟通，及时反馈绩效考核的所有问题，真正地帮助企业落实每一项绩效考核工作，提升员工的绩效和满意度。
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
资产管理
<div class="modal fade" id="project-9" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-9-label" aria-hidden="true">
帮助企业主动管理整个IT资产库，提供资产自动发现、资产跟踪、配置管理、软件许可管理、软件使用监控、采购与合同管理等功能，对资产的整个生命周期实现全程的管理。从而帮助企业全面掌握资产的分布以及运行状况，达到降低成本和提高运营效率的目的。
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
企业邮局
<div class="modal fade" id="project-10" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-10-label" aria-hidden="true">
尚石自主研发的大型企业邮件系统，经过10年的深入研发和完善，系统技术成熟，性能稳定高效，能充分发挥邮件服务器性能，是众多知名企业及政府高校搭建邮件服务器系统及企业邮箱的首选方案
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
知识管理
<div class="modal fade" id="project-11" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-11-label" aria-hidden="true">
借助知识管理平台对组织内外的知识进行有效的获取、沉淀、共享、应用、学习和创新，从而提高员工的素质和技能、企业的执行力，通过有效多途径的方式来积累知识和共享知识；使人与知识紧密结合，保证能够在最需要的时间将最需要的知识传送给最需要的人。
<button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">关闭</button>
制度管理
<div class="modal fade" id="project-12" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="project-12-label" aria-hidden="true">
借助工作流，在固化部分流程的同时，真正做到流程流转随需而设；让员工在执行制度过程中简洁、有效，充分体验制度的人性化，让员工在面对相同事务时能自发的执行制度，在实践中把企业制度有效地执行落地。
尚石开发的OA系统，让我们的内外沟通、协同办公及流程审批更加高效便捷，多个应用模块业务系统无缝集成，引领了一站式的工作体验。
感谢尚石以有趣便捷的参与形式，为我司搭建员工微笑交流平台，展现上万员工的精神面貌，号召员工“微笑工作，快乐生活”，让员工有获得感，让企业有凝聚力。
对原有系统的系统架构、数据结构、系统逻辑、业务功能等实现完美割接，实现一套完善、高效的系统建设，具有丰富的大数量流程重建项目经验。
十三年系统开发经验，客户涵盖多个行业领域

About CentOS:

The Community ENTerprise Operating System (CentOS) Linux is a community-supported enterprise distribution derived from sources freely provided to the public by Red Hat. As such CentOS Linux aims to be functionally compatible with Red Hat Enterprise Linux. The CentOS Project is the organization that builds CentOS. We mainly change packages to remove upstream vendor branding and artwork.

For information on CentOS please visit the CentOS website.

2015年 铭飞MCms获得最热门开源项目第40位
国内开源 java cms，铭飞MCms
第一阶段：预习
观看百度学院里的网站建设视频课程，对网站建设流程有一个初步的了解。认识html语言，div+css布局等一些建站基础知识。百度成立于2010年，至今已经发展成为国内最大的模板分享平台，为广大网站建设从业者提供了方便和帮助。我们拥有大量优质的建站资源，资源市场价值上万元。在这里聚集了大量网络从业人员，提供来自全国各地、不同行业的资源与人脉。
第二阶段：上课
百度老师通过QQ群远程教学，全面系统的给大家讲解建站知识。内容涉及网站搭建，网站优化，模板开发等最新建站技术。
第三阶段：实践
自己搭建一个网站并开发一套模板，碰到不理解或不会的，可以咨询我们在线QQ辅导员，我们每天8小时在线提供顾问式指导。

Canadian Property Tax Association Inc.

Founded in 1967 the Canadian Property Tax Association Inc. is a national organization providing a forum for the exchange of ideas and information relating to both commercial and industrial property tax issues arising across Canada.

L’Association canadienne de taxe foncière Inc. est une association d'envergure nationale qui préconise l'échange d'idées et favorise la diffusion d'informations en matière de fiscalité municipale relativement à des immeubles à vocation commerciale et industrielle.
<div id="block-block-1" class="block block-block first last odd">

The Canadian Property Tax Association brings together a uniquely qualified array of top corporate property tax officers lawyers tax consultants and government officials. Membership in this association will be of tangible benefit to you and your organization.

column1: This page is used to test the proper operation of the Apache HTTP server after it has been installed. If you can read this page it means that the Apache HTTP server installed at this site is working properly.
If you are a member of the general public:
The fact that you are seeing this page indicates that the website you just visited is either experiencing problems or is undergoing routine maintenance.

If you would like to let the administrators of this website know that you've seen this page instead of the page you expected you should send them e-mail. In general mail sent to the name "webmaster" and directed to the website's domain should reach the appropriate person.
For example if you experienced problems while visiting www.example.com you should send e-mail to "webmaster@example.com".

You may now add content to the directory /var/www/html/. Note that until you do so people visiting your website will see this page and not your content. To prevent this page from ever being used follow the instructions in the file /etc/httpd/conf.d/welcome.conf.
You are free to use the images below on Apache and CentOS Linux powered HTTP servers. Thanks for using Apache and CentOS!

About CentOS:

The Community ENTerprise Operating System (CentOS) Linux is a community-supported enterprise distribution derived from sources freely provided to the public by Red Hat. As such CentOS Linux aims to be functionally compatible with Red Hat Enterprise Linux. The CentOS Project is the organization that builds CentOS. We mainly change packages to remove upstream vendor branding and artwork.

For information on CentOS please visit the CentOS website.

Note:

CentOS is an Operating System and it is used to power this website

Unless this server is on the centos.org domain the CentOS Project doesn't have anything to do with the content on this webserver or any e-mails that directed you to this site.

In need of a web/cloud software engineer? I excel at backend technologies but I&rsquo
column2: m not too bad with frontend tech either.

column1: Have a look through some of the kinds projects I&rsquo
column2: ve worked on in the past:

column1: <div class="db pv4 ph3 ph0-l no-underline dark-gray">
Developed a REST API using Golang (go) for Democracy Live&rsquo
column2: s new web applications. It is the backbone that powers all their current efforts which together enable us to import many different data specifications into our system  edit and/or translate data to our customer&rsquo
column3: s wishes  and finally publish it to customer websites  or export it into other auxilary systems. The api I built is much more efficient and flexible than the older Drupal-based system we are depricating  and runs with less than half the cpu and memory requirements  even though our admin user load has increased.

column1: read more
<div class="db pv4 ph3 ph0-l no-underline dark-gray">

Architected and developed a system to scrape data off ballot PDF files into structured ballot content which could be QAed and used for accessible  internationalized sample ballots  augmented with voter guide information  or exported for use in other related systems.
The data was scraped from the pdfs via a scalable microservice built on Flask/Python3 consisting of blob storage (s3 or azure)  and Redis for pub/sub &amp
column3: s API was used heavily in the pdf parsing and processing where an xml dump didn&rsquo

column1: read more
<div class="db pv4 ph3 ph0-l no-underline dark-gray">
Blind Accessible (WCAG 2.0) and Multilingual Sample Ballot and Voter Guide

Developed significant enhancements to our existing Online Ballot  Sample Ballot and Voter Guide products to make them WCAG 2.0 compliant and multilingual. Besides learning about Aria attributes and WCAG 2.0 compliance and implementing them  templates were moved out of drupal/php into handlebars (similar to mustache) templates  and rendered client side from JSON data representing the ballots  which was cached and loaded from Azure Blob Storage. This meant much less load on our servers  and quicker page loads on average for our users  while enabling more people to get ballot information.

column1: If you're seeing this page via a web browser it means you've setup Tomcat successfully. Congratulations!

Tomcat8 veterans might be pleased to learn that this system instance of Tomcat is installed with CATALINA_HOME in /usr/share/tomcat8 and CATALINA_BASE in /var/lib/tomcat8 following the rules from /usr/share/doc/tomcat8-common/RUNNING.txt.gz.
You might consider installing the following packages if you haven't already done so:
tomcat8-docs: This package installs a web application that allows to browse the Tomcat 8 documentation locally. Once installed you can access it by clicking here.
tomcat8-examples: This package installs a web application that allows to access the Tomcat 8 Servlet and JSP examples. Once installed you can access it by clicking here.
tomcat8-admin: This package installs two web applications that can help managing this Tomcat instance. Once installed you can access the manager webapp and the host-manager webapp.

NOTE: For security reasons using the manager webapp is restricted to users with role "manager-gui". The host-manager webapp is restricted to users with role "admin-gui". Users are defined in /etc/tomcat8/tomcat-users.xml.

You can find more info in the FAQs section or check the HOW-TO Guides for getting started with PHP applications.

XAMPP is meant only for development purposes. It has certain configuration settings that make it easy to develop locally but that are insecure if you want to have your installation accessible to others.

If you want have your XAMPP accessible from the internet make sure you understand the implications and you checked the FAQs to learn how to protect your site. Alternatively you can use WAMP MAMP or LAMP which are similar packages which are more suitable for production.
Start the XAMPP Control Panel to check the server status.

Welcome To CarbonNano An Internet Of Things Company.
CarbonNano designs manufactures and sells Internet of Things products that provide peace of mind solutions for your home garden or office that are easily consumer installed.
Our products are cost effective have multiple uses and have a very long battery life. There is no need for anyone to visit your home or office to install our products you can easily do this yourself!
Please browse through our Products page and our Product FAQs page for further information.
CarbonNano also provides design and manufacturing services to individuals and companies.
We can offer cost effective robust solutions for your ideas we have a wealth of experience of keeping things simple
please browse through our Services page for further information.
Have An Idea For A Product or Software?
If you have an idea CarbonNano can help to make that idea a reality. Rather than showing a Customer or Investor just a glossy presentation
why not also have functional working prototype? You are much more likely to secure your investment with working prototypes for a demonstration.
We offer full concept to prototype to volume manufacture design services please browse through our Services page for further information.

What is Censys?

Censys is a platform that helps information security practitioners discover monitor and analyze devices that are accessible from the Internet. We regularly probe every public IP address and popular domain names curate and enrich the resulting data and make it intelligible through an interactive search engine and API.

column1: Enterprises use Censys to understand their network attack surfaces. CERTs and security researchers use it to discover new threats and assess their global impact. Censys was founded by computer scientists at the University of Michigan and data we collect has been used in hundreds of scientific papers by researchers around the world.

One way that Censys finds publicly-reachable devices is by using Internet-wide scanning. We make a small number of harmless connection attempts to every IPv4 address worldwide each day. When we discover that a computer or device is configured to accept connections we follow up by completing protocol handshakes to learn more about the running services.

We never attempt to bypass any technical barriers exploit security problems or otherwise access non-public-facing services and we follow community best practices to reduce any burden on remote networks. The only data we receive is information that is publicly visible to anyone who connects to a particular address and port.
For technical information about the kinds of data Censys collects visit our data definitions page.
Censys scans the Internet from the 198.108.66.0/23 subnet which you can whitelist or blacklist if you wish.
We sometimes make follow-up connections from other machines at dynamic IP addresses but blocking the addresses above is sufficient to prevent your device from appearing in our IPv4 dataset.

Censys data is sometimes used by researchers and network administrators to detect security problems and alert the operators of vulnerable systems. If you block our scans you might not receive these important security notifications.
If you have questions about Censys scanning please get in touch at support@censys.io.

About CentOS:

The Community ENTerprise Operating System (CentOS) Linux is a community-supported enterprise distribution derived from sources freely provided to the public by Red Hat. As such CentOS Linux aims to be functionally compatible with Red Hat Enterprise Linux. The CentOS Project is the organization that builds CentOS. We mainly change packages to remove upstream vendor branding and artwork.

For information on CentOS please visit the CentOS website.

If you're seeing this page via a web browser it means you've setup Tomcat successfully. Congratulations!
This is the default Tomcat home page. It can be found on the local filesystem at: /var/lib/tomcat7/webapps/ROOT/index.html

Tomcat7 veterans might be pleased to learn that this system instance of Tomcat is installed with CATALINA_HOME in /usr/share/tomcat7 and CATALINA_BASE in /var/lib/tomcat7 following the rules from /usr/share/doc/tomcat7-common/RUNNING.txt.gz.
You might consider installing the following packages if you haven't already done so:
tomcat7-docs: This package installs a web application that allows to browse the Tomcat 7 documentation locally. Once installed you can access it by clicking here.
tomcat7-examples: This package installs a web application that allows to access the Tomcat 7 Servlet and JSP examples. Once installed you can access it by clicking here.
tomcat7-admin: This package installs two web applications that can help managing this Tomcat instance. Once installed you can access the manager webapp and the host-manager webapp.

NOTE: For security reasons using the manager webapp is restricted to users with role "manager-gui". The host-manager webapp is restricted to users with role "admin-gui". Users are defined in /etc/tomcat7/tomcat-users.xml.

ขอขอบพระคุณ บริษัท เจริญโภคภัณฑ์อาหาร จำกัด (มหาชน) ที่กรุณาไว้วางใจเลือกใช้บริการรักษาความปลอดภัยของเรา ทางทีมงานและพนักงานรักษาความปลอดภัยของบริษัทจะตั้งใจทำงานอย่างเต็มที่และดูแลท่านอย่างดีที่สุดตลอดไป...We proud to serve you.

เราได้ออกแบบและพัฒนา Software และ Application เพื่อตรวจสอบการทำงานรักษาความปลอดภัยให้กับผู้ว่าจ้าง ทำให้มั่นใจได้ว่าการตรวจตราบริเวณพื้นที่รับผิดชอบที่ทางผู้ว่าจ้างได้มอบหมายนั้น พนักรักษาความปลอดภัยของเราปฏิบัติจริง ตรวจตราโดยละเอียด ส่งข้อมูลแบบ Real Time และมั่นใจได้ว่าพนักงานรักษาความปลอดภัยไม่หลับแน่นอนในขณะปฏิบัติหน้าที่

Welcome to the Eastbourne and Wealden RAYNET Group website.                    <HR COLOR='BLUE'>

Update 18 March 2020 - Coronavirus

The Eastbourne & Wealden RAYNET Group will not be providing Communications for community events for the foreseeable due to the Lockdown caused by the Coronavirus. However the Group is active on the air from home and mobile on 144.675 MHz on Fridays see below and Mondays at 14:00 hrs.

The Eastbourne & Wealden RAYNET Group was formed in 1976 with the objective of supporting the blue light emergency services Emergency Planning Officer and the voluntary emergency services such as the British Red Cross and the St John Ambulance. To read more about RAYNET in general follow this link: About RAYNET.

Eastbourne & Wealden RAYNET Group holds a weekly radio "check in" on Fridays at 19:30 hours (clock time) on a frequency of 144.675MHz.

The Eastbourne & Wealden RAYNET Group works in partnership with Sussex Police East Sussex Fire & Rescue Service the East Sussex Hospitals Trust St John Ambulance the British Red Cross the East Sussex Resilience Partnership and District and Borough Emergency Planning Teams.

In support of these organisations the Eastbourne & Wealden RAYNET Group provides communications during emergencies and at local community charity events such as the Eastbourne Half Marathon Ardingly Triathlon and the Action Medical Research Southdowns Walk.

Since 2001 the Group has provided over 19 700 operator hours supporting a total of 310 emergencies and community events. To see past event reports follow this link : Event Reports

If you are organising an event and you would like to know if RAYNET can assist you follow this link: Information for event organisers.

If you are interested in joining RAYNET follow this link Joining RAYNET
